ingredients_text: 32% wheat flour, water, sourdough (9% rye flour, water), 6.5% whole grain rye flour, 4% flax seeds, 4% barley flakes, 3% sunflower seeds, 2.5% rye flour,  yeast, salt, 0.8% oatmeal, caramel sugar syrup, barley malt extract, wheat protein, invert sugar, barley malt flour, acidity regulator: sodium acetates;  preservative: sorbic acid;  natural aroma, ethyl alcohol.  Alcohol content 1.5%.  THE FOOD IS NOT SUITABLE FOR CHILDREN.  May contain traces of soy, lupine, mustard and sesame.
